<refsect1><title>DESCRIPTION</title>
<para>
  This is a general utility library for writing (generally) single-threaded
  servers using a simple event loop.
</para>
<para>
  Besides a main loop which use various system-level
  interfaces efficiently (select, poll, kqueue),
  we have support for thread pooling and we use Gtk+ version 1.2's object
  system (See <ulink url="http://www.gtk.org/">the Gtk Home Page</ulink>).
</para>
</refsect1>

